{{Quote|Sonny, energizing an anticoncussion field is ''not'' like hot-wiring somebody's skyhopper and going for a joy-ride!|Klaus "Doc" Vandangante|<ref name="Han Solo at Stars' End">''[[Han Solo at Stars' End]]''</ref>}}
An '''anticoncussion field''' was a highly advanced type of [[Force field/Legends|force field]] used at the [[Stars' End/Legends|Stars' End]] prison facility.

==Characteristics==
Anticoncussion fields were generated by projectors such as the [[Rampart-class anticoncussion generator|''Rampart''-class anticoncussion generator]]. The projectors honeycombed the interior of the building it was designed to protect. When activated, the field dramatically improved the integrity of floors, walls, ceilings and other internal surfaces. The projector's umbrella-shaped [[Magnetic field/Legends|magnetic fields]] created a single cohesive anticoncussion field that absorbed and dispersed kinetic energy. The field was powerful enough to render blasts, collisions, and other impacts inert.<ref name="EGWT">''[[The Essential Guide to Weapons and Technology]]''</ref>

